org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.statistics

Interface DefaultStatisticsProvider

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AttributeIndexImpl, CustomAttributeIndex, CustomIndex, CustomNameIndex, FeatureDataAdapter, IndexImpl, NullIndex, RasterDataAdapter

    public interface DefaultStatisticsProvider
    This interface can be used with data type adapters and indices so that default statistics will be added to the data store when the adapter/index is added.

    • Method Summary
